      'privacy.s12.table.r7c3': 'Adjust App settings, cookie preferences, or contact DPO',
      'privacy.s12.table.r8c1': 'Complaint',
      'privacy.s12.table.r8c2': 'Lodge a complaint with a supervisory authority',
      'privacy.s12.table.r8c3': 'Contact your local data protection authority',
      'privacy.s12.title': '12. Your privacy rights — overview',
      'privacy.s13.p': 'EEA residents may contact their local supervisory authority if they believe our processing violates GDPR. You also have the right not to be subject to decisions based solely on automated processing that produce legal or similarly significant effects, except where permitted by law with appropriate safeguards.',
      'privacy.s13.title': '13. EEA rights and supervisory authorities',
      'privacy.s14.l1': '<strong>Right to know',
      'privacy.s14.l2': '<strong>Right to delete',
      'privacy.s14.l3': '<strong>Right to correct',
      'privacy.s14.l4': '<strong>Right to opt out',
      'privacy.s14.l5': '<strong>Right to limit',
      'privacy.s14.l6': '<strong>Right to non-discrimination',
      'privacy.s14.p': 'If you are a California resident, the California Consumer Privacy Act (CCPA) as amended by the California Privacy Rights Act (CPRA) provides additional rights:',
      'privacy.s14.p2': 'Submit California requests to support@pinfoldai.com with subject &ldquo;California Privacy Request.&rdquo; Authorized agents may submit requests with proof of authorization. We will verify identity before responding.',
      'privacy.s14.title': '14. California (CCPA / CPRA)',
      'privacy.s15.p': 'If you are in Brazil, the Lei Geral de ProteÃ§Ã£o de Dados (LGPD) grants rights including confirmation of processing, access, correction, anonymization or deletion, portability, information about sharing, revocation of consent, and review of automated decisions. Our legal bases under LGPD include consent, contract performance, legitimate interests, credit protection, and compliance with legal obligations. Contact our DPO to exercise LGPD rights or raise concerns with the Autoridade Nacional de ProteÃ§Ã£o de Dados (ANPD).',
      'privacy.s15.title': '15. Brazil (LGPD)',
      'privacy.s16.p': 'If you are in Canada, personal information is handled in accordance with the Personal Information Protection and Electronic Documents Act (PIPEDA) and applicable provincial laws. You may access, correct, and challenge our compliance by contacting support@pinfoldai.com. You may also contact the Office of the Privacy Commissioner of Canada if concerns are unresolved.',
      'privacy.s16.title': '16. Canada (PIPEDA)',
      'privacy.s17.p': 'If you are in Australia, we handle personal information in accordance with the Privacy Act 1988 and the Australian Privacy Principles (APPs). You may request access to or correction of personal information we hold. Complaints may be submitted to us first; if unresolved, you may contact the Office of the Australian Information Commissioner (OAIC).',
      'privacy.s17.title': '17. Australia (Privacy Act 1988)',
      'privacy.s18.p': 'AI features may process text, file metadata, or excerpts you submit to generate suggestions, captions, or organizational recommendations. Processing may occur on-device or on our servers hosted on Azure or Hetzner infrastructure. We may log prompts and outputs in limited form for safety, quality assurance, and abuse prevention. We do not use your private file library to train public AI models without explicit consent. Review AI outputs before use; automated suggestions are not guaranteed to be accurate.',
      'privacy.s18.title': '18. AI and automated processing',
      'privacy.s19.p': 'Our website uses cookies and similar technologies as described in our <a href="/legal/cookies.html">Cookie Policy',
      'privacy.s19.title': '19. Cookies and similar technologies',
      'privacy.s2.p': 'This policy covers personal data we process when you use the App, create an Account, connect Third-Party Services, purchase a Subscription, visit our website, or contact support. It does not cover Third-Party Services you connect (Google, Apple, Facebook, cloud providers, social platforms, app stores, Stripe), which have their own privacy policies. See also our <a href="/legal/cookies.html">Cookie Policy',
      'privacy.s2.title': '2. Scope and linked policies',
      'privacy.s20.p': 'Pinfold is not directed at children under 13 (or under 16 in the EEA/UK where applicable). We do not knowingly collect personal data from children. If you believe a child has provided personal data, contact support@pinfoldai.com and we will take steps to delete it.',
      'privacy.s20.title': '20. Children&rsquo;s privacy',
      'privacy.s21.p': '<strong>Data Protection Officer (DPO):',
      'privacy.s21.title': '21. Data Protection Officer',
      'privacy.s22.p': 'Our website does not currently respond to browser &ldquo;Do Not Track&rdquo; signals because no uniform standard exists. Where required by law, we honor Global Privacy Control (GPC) signals for opt-out of sale/sharing — note that we do not sell personal data. See our Cookie Policy for website preference controls.',
      'privacy.s22.title': '22. Do not track and global privacy control',
      'privacy.s23.p': 'We may update this Privacy Policy to reflect changes in our practices, technology, or legal requirements. Material changes will be indicated by updating the version date above and, where required, by in-App notice or email. We encourage you to review this policy periodically.',
      'privacy.s23.title': '23. Changes to this policy',
      'privacy.s24.p': '<strong>Privacy inquiries:',
      'privacy.s24.title': '24. Contact',
      'privacy.s3.note': 'Local files on your Device are generally processed on-device. We do not upload your entire file library unless you explicitly use cloud sync, social publishing, or AI features that require server processing.',
