      'third-party.s2.infra.l5': 'Open source libraries — see <a href="/legal/open-source.html">Open Source Software Notice',
      'third-party.s2.infra.title': 'Infrastructure &amp; technology',
      'third-party.s2.p': 'The Service may integrate with or depend on providers including, without limitation:',
      'third-party.s2.payment.l1': 'Google Play Billing',
      'third-party.s2.payment.l2': 'Apple App Store In-App Purchases',
      'third-party.s2.payment.l3': 'Stripe (for web or direct billing where offered)',
      'third-party.s2.payment.title': 'Payments &amp; subscriptions',
      'third-party.s2.social.l1': 'Meta (Facebook, Instagram, Threads)',
      'third-party.s2.social.l2': 'Google (including YouTube)',
      'third-party.s2.social.l3': 'Microsoft (including LinkedIn where available)',
      'third-party.s2.social.l4': 'TikTok, X (formerly Twitter), and other supported networks',
      'third-party.s2.social.title': 'Social &amp; publishing platforms',
      'third-party.s2.title': '2. Categories of Third-Party Services',
      'third-party.s3.p': 'Reference to any Third-Party Service, logo, or trademark does not constitute endorsement, sponsorship, or affiliation\n  unless expressly stated in writing. Platform icons and names are used solely to identify integrations you may choose\n  to enable.',
      'third-party.s3.title': '3. No endorsement',
      'third-party.s4.p': 'Third-Party Services may experience outages, degraded performance, API changes, geographic restrictions, or\n  discontinuation. Pinfold is not responsible for failures, delays, or errors caused by Third-Party Services, including\n  failed scheduled posts, sync interruptions, or authentication failures.',
      'third-party.s4.title': '4. Availability and performance',
      'third-party.s5.p': 'When you enable an integration, we and the Third-Party Service may exchange data necessary to provide the feature —\n  such as OAuth tokens, profile identifiers, file metadata, or media you choose to publish. Each provider&rsquo;s privacy\n  policy describes how they handle that data. See our <a href="/legal/privacy.html">Privacy Policy',
      'third-party.s5.title': '5. Data shared with third parties',
      'third-party.s6.p': 'Third-Party Services may charge separate fees. Subscription purchases through Google Play, Apple, or Stripe are\n  processed by those providers and subject to their refund and billing policies. Pinfold does not control store billing\n  decisions or chargeback outcomes.',
      'third-party.s6.title': '6. Fees and billing',
      'third-party.s7.p': 'Third-Party Services may suspend or terminate your account, revoke API access, or remove content according to their\n  rules. Pinfold is not liable for platform enforcement actions. See our\n  <a href="/legal/social-integration.html">Social Platform Integration Policy',
      'third-party.s7.title': '7. Platform enforcement',
      'third-party.s8.p': 'AI features may rely on external model providers. Those providers may process inputs under their own terms. AI output\n  may be inaccurate or inappropriate. See our <a href="/legal/ai-disclaimer.html">AI Disclaimer',
      'third-party.s8.title': '8. AI providers',
      'third-party.s9.p': 'The Service or our website may contain links to external websites. We are not responsible for the content, security,\n  or privacy practices of linked sites. Access external sites at your own risk.',
      'third-party.s9.title': '9. Links to external sites',
      'third-party.seealso': 'See also:\n  <a href="/legal/terms.html">Terms of Service',
      'third-party.title': 'Third-Party Services Disclaimer',
      'warranty.intro': 'This Warranty Disclaimer (&ldquo;Disclaimer&rdquo;) applies to Pinfold (the &ldquo;App&rdquo;), our website, APIs at <a href="https://api.pinfoldai.com">api.pinfoldai.com',
      'warranty.meta': 'Last updated: July 6, 2026 · Version 2026-07-06',
      'warranty.s1.p': 'THE SERVICE IS PROVIDED ON AN &ldquo;AS IS&rdquo; AND &ldquo;AS AVAILABLE&rdquo; BASIS, WITH ALL FAULTS. TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY APPLICABLE LAW, WE DISCLAIM ALL WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, WHETHER EXPRESS, IMPLIED, STATUTORY, OR OTHERWISE, INCLUDING ANY IMPLIED WARRANTIES OF MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, TITLE, QUIET ENJOYMENT, ACCURACY, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.',
      'warranty.s1.title': '1. AS IS and AS AVAILABLE',
      'warranty.s10.p': 'If you are dissatisfied with the Service, your sole and exclusive remedy is to stop using the Service and, where applicable, cancel your subscription. Our liability is further limited as described in our <a href="/legal/liability.html">Limitation of Liability',
      'warranty.s10.title': '10. Sole remedy',
      'warranty.s11.p': 'Questions: <a href="mailto:support@pinfoldai.com">support@pinfoldai.com',
      'warranty.s11.title': '11. Contact',
      'warranty.s2.l1': 'The Service will meet your requirements or expectations',
      'warranty.s2.l2': 'The Service will be uninterrupted, timely, secure, or error-free',
      'warranty.s2.l3': 'Results obtained from the Service (including AI output) will be accurate, complete, or reliable',
      'warranty.s2.l4': 'Defects or errors will be corrected within any particular timeframe',
      'warranty.s2.l5': 'Third-party integrations (social, cloud, payment) will remain available or unchanged',
      'warranty.s2.l6': 'Files or data will never be lost, corrupted, or deleted',
      'warranty.s2.p': 'We do not warrant that:',
      'warranty.s2.title': '2. No guarantee of performance',
      'warranty.s3.p': 'AI-assisted features may produce incorrect, incomplete, biased, or offensive content. We disclaim all warranties regarding AI output. You are solely responsible for reviewing and verifying AI-generated content before use. See our <a href="/legal/ai-disclaimer.html">AI Disclaimer',
      'warranty.s3.title': '3. AI and automated features',
      'warranty.s4.p': 'The Service integrates with third-party platforms and may display third-party content or links. We do not warrant and are not responsible for third-party services, their availability, security, or content. Your use of third-party services is at your own risk and subject to their terms.',
      'warranty.s4.title': '4. Third-party services and content',
      'warranty.s5.p': 'Features labeled beta, preview, experimental, or similar are provided without warranty of any kind and may be modified or discontinued at any time without notice.',
      'warranty.s5.title': '5. Beta and experimental features',
      'warranty.s6.p': 'We do not warrant compatibility with all devices, operating system versions, or network configurations. You are responsible for maintaining supported hardware, software, and connectivity.',
      'warranty.s6.title': '6. Device and environment',
      'warranty.s7.p': 'While we implement reasonable security measures, we do not warrant that the Service is free from viruses, malware, unauthorized access, or other harmful components. See our <a href="/legal/security.html">Security Disclaimer',
      'warranty.s7.title': '7. Security',
